Frontend rrt_max increased massively across pods, indicating cascading effects.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Conclusion\nThe root cause appears to be centered around `AdService` which showed critical latency spikes and increased error rates, affecting its interaction with `Frontend` and potentially other dependent services. Further investigation into `AdService` infrastructure and resource allocation may be necessary to ensure stability."}
